---
/**
 * Componente ManifestoIA.astro
 * Representa la filosofía de uso de IA del profesional.
 * Nota: Se han extraído los SVGs directamente para evitar conflictos de importación en el entorno de previsualización.
 */
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-[#080B14]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto opacity-0 translate-y-10 animate-fade-in-up">
    <!-- Etiqueta Superior -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.1)]"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="14"
          height="14"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-blue-400"
          ><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg
        >
        <span
          class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[3px] text-blue-400"
          >Filosofía de Desarrollo</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contenedor Principal Estilo "Glass-Panel" -->
    <div class="relative group">
      <!-- Brillos decorativos traseros -->
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-1 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 rounded-4xl blur opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-25 transition duration-1000"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative bg-[#0d121f]/80 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-4xl p-8 md:p-16 overflow-hidden text-left"
      >
        <!-- Decoración de cuadrícula de fondo -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none"
          style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <!-- Iconografía Central: La Fusión -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
            <div
              class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/40"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"></rect><rect
                  x="9"
                  y="9"
                  width="6"
                  height="6"></rect><path d="M15 2v2"></path><path d="M15 20v2"
                ></path><path d="M2 15h2"></path><path d="M2 9h2"></path><path
                  d="M20 15h2"></path><path d="M20 9h2"></path><path d="M9 2v2"
                ></path><path d="M9 20v2"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="h-px w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-transparent"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 text-blue-400 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"
                ></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><polyline
                  points="16 11 18 13 22 9"></polyline></svg
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- El Texto de Impacto -->
          <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1]"
          >
            Aprovecho la <span
              class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-400 animate-pulse-glow"
              >inteligencia artificial</span
            > para acelerar tareas repetitivas, pero siempre entiendo y valido cada
            cambio.
          </h2>

          <p
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/60 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto italic"
          >
            "Utilizo la IA como apoyo, <span
              class="text-white font-semibold not-italic border-b-2 border-blue-500/50"
              >no como reemplazo</span
            > de mi criterio profesional."
          </p>

          <!-- Footer del Manifiesto: Garantía de Calidad -->
          <div
            class="mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-white/5 w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#10b981"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"
                ></path><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"></polyline></svg
              >
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                >Código Auditado</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#10b981"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"
                ></path><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"></polyline></svg
              >
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                >Arquitectura Consciente</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#10b981"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"
                ></path><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"></polyline></svg
              >
              <span
                class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                >Validación Humana</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Texto pequeño aclaratorio debajo -->
    <p
      class="text-center mt-8 text-[10px] text-white/20 uppercase tracking-[4px] font-medium"
    >
      Eficiencia en la ejecución — Rigor en la decisión
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }

  .animate-pulse-glow {
    animation: pulseGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes pulseGlow {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5));
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.8;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.8));
    }
  }
</style>
